headline: Why SoFi (SOFI) Shares Are Getting Obliterated Today
summary: Shares of digital financial services company SoFi Technologies (NASDAQ:SOFI) fell 5.3% in the afternoon session after investors took some profits off the table as markets awaited signals on future monetary policy from the Federal Reserve's Jackson Hole symposium later in the week.
